data-triple-N3.o: "2011 was a common year that started on a Saturday in the Gregorian calendar. It was the 2011th year of the Common Era (CE) and Anno Domini (AD) designations; the 11th year of the 3rd millennium and of the 21st century; and the 2nd of the 2010s. The United Nations designated 2011 as the International Year of Forests and the International Year of Chemistry."@en
